[Requirements]

- Gauche 0.8.14 or later.
- FUSE 2.6 or later.
  These can be downloaded from http://fuse.sourceforge.net/ .

[Usage of sample programs]

  $ mkdir /tmp/fs

* Hello World file system
  $ example/hello.scm /tmp/fs

* Fusexmp file system
  $ example/fusexmp.scm /tmp/fs

* Outputz file system
  $ example/outputz.scm -k=SECRET_KEY -m=/tmp/fs
